<informationtext name="Information">
<![CDATA[
<p>The faculty for environmental policy analysis &amp; planning offers the following minor. The Environmental Policy Analysis &amp; Planning minor is for natural and social science students desiring basic training in policy analysis theory and methods.</p>
<h2>Minor Advisor</h2>
<p>G. Arnold (Environmental Science &amp; Policy)</p>
]]>
</informationtext>
