<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Do you want to explore the relationships among the environment, law, policy, people, and community planning? Students apply coursework in natural sciences to analyze environmental problems and formulate policy options and solutions.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
